{"tid":1533301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【學界林鄭】大埔何郭佩珍中學校長梁秋雲 惡行難洗","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:14:04.000Z","uid":67391,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7fe5ce027a350d62b1fb9ccf5c52b97c1c535a","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"【學界林鄭】大埔何郭佩珍中學校長梁秋雲 惡行難洗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何郭佩珍學生們</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">You are not alone</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最為人所知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n紅白藍革命</span><br />\n發生時間:2003~2007年<br />\n<br />\n惡行1:<br />\n自己著皮草，Gucci鞋，唔俾學生揹名牌，最後迫到學生揹紅白藍返學<br />\n<br />\n最後又話學生標奇立異記缺點<br />\n<br />\n惡行2: 涉嫌種族歧視<br />\n發生時間: 2003~2007年<br />\n唔俾學生染髮，但有混血學生頭髮天生金都要迫染黑<br />\n家長寫埋信証明都要染<br />\n<br />\n利申: 2003~2007 舊生<br />\n上面2樣係當事人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 呼籲聽日9月3日早上七至八點及下午一點學校門口聲援<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 何中舊生聯署聲明🙏🙏🙏麻煩大家, 簽完再fw俾自己班其他班其他form嘅同學仔<br />\n仁人仁政 拒絕滅聲 thanks! <br />\n<br />\n同學仔, 我知大家好肉緊<br />\n但個聯署簽一次就好喇<br />\n同埋用真名<br />\n份野send埋比教育局同記者架<br />\n假名比人笑膠我哋<br />\n無謂加重back end同學嘅工作量啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeBU9Zv4tF9UjVvyYluY9PKT99Q2SLleyWrepi2U-5_nwXr5Q/viewform?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeBU9Zv4tF9UjVvyYluY9PKT99Q2SLleyWrepi2U-5_nwXr5Q%2Fviewform%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=8cd50c49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeBU9Zv4tF9UjVvyYluY9PKT99Q2SLleyWrepi2U-5_nwXr5Q/viewform?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"9db3a45bf83c41dddc549300ecba4bf4b5daea8a","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"92abdfcac671a85652a66e146ba886759ba08a4b","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f9032f8ef3109484b889d88a9c826b5c5f0a3767","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"e7dee6a995702676062af5fcfc2beff4f8d04c32","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:35.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"b20fee81da451f1a47bc8fef11534bd5e400a81d","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"56339f56a91fbec38c09740c4f5e3bbb2fd7e5b5","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"09d12f5d655672d1061c131c2405d436210ad6e9","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"c49fd27e25d1c7daaf2ed95e45621e1f85107062","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"d1a626c42b581d0b0547638618afab371a101239","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"2a5204a989b191c3df0aae5158c8c0b5701a9ac4","tid":1533301,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"0fb66ce256f75e9999ff2597085bb32baef8fa6e","tid":1533301,"uid":